      "text": "The anger about Alain Berset's Sunday interview radiates far beyond Europe. But not in French-speaking Switzerland, where there is a great deal of understanding for the president. Berset himself is now trying to explain himself. (Basler Zeitung, Wednesday, March 15, 2023, p. 3)"
