    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "9004d7aab4cdcc7a",
      "text": "He has said it before, a little more than a week ago. \"L'ivresse de la guerre me préoccupe beaucoup,\" was the title of a long interview in \"Le Temps,\" [https://www.letemps.ch/suisse/alain-berset-livresse-guerre-me-preoccupe-beaucoup page] in which President Alain Berset spoke at length about the war in Ukraine and Switzerland's role. \"The war frenzy concerns me a lot.\" Berset elaborated in the interview that he is concerned about the warlike climate that currently prevails all over the world, including in Switzerland. \"One has the impression that some actors, even former pacifists, are carried away as if by the frenzy of war.\""
