      "id": "88b555b83648d77b",
      "text": "Then, a week later, another interview with Berset, this time in the \"NZZ am Sonntag\". \"I sense a war frenzy in certain circles today,\" was the title. Berset explained that the current climate reminded him of the climate at the beginning of the First World War. \"The prevailing opinion at the time was that there were so many tensions and frustrations that this could only be discharged in a war.\"\n\nThe interview appeared, and it happened: all at the same time."
